subject: Track and Field
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: Allyson Felix and Jeneba Tarmoh, who tied for third place in the women’s 100-meter race at the Olympic trials, have to decide how to settle the matter — bow out, flip a coin or race in a runoff.
